  "3331090": {
    "name": "Fall in Flowers - フォール イン フラワーズ",
    "steam_appid": 3331090,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3331090/extras/f6869e7dea31b7e22fb5632b3121535e.avif?t=1769911795\" width=1500 height=400 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>Story</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">和平思想与大型组织“盐与玻璃”的实际控制。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">在这个反乌托邦世界中濒临死亡的少年哈拉萨，幸运地获得了一份工作。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">在花园里捡垃圾的工作，每天为了生存而赚取必要的盐。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">在那里遇到了一个有着美丽红发的小精灵女孩。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">她似乎在寻找什么。从这次相遇开始展开的故事，</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">这个阴暗的世界会被改变，还是只是昙花一现？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3331090/extras/433324860ae276b2299c65c8dae36152.webp?t=1769911795\" width=900 height=1 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>▼      System      ▼</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3331090/extras/433324860ae276b2299c65c8dae36152.webp?t=1769911795\" width=900 height=1 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>◆ 在随机生成的地图中自由穿梭</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每局游戏都会随机生成地图，玩家需在其中进行3D跑酷动作！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3331090/extras/3952d85e2d20c302d1051c4595430512.poster.avif?t=1769911795\" width=780 height=334 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3331090/extras/3952d85e2d20c302d1051c4595430512.webm?t=1769911795\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3331090/extras/3952d85e2d20c302d1051c4595430512.mp4?t=1769911795\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>◆ 将坠落伤害转化为力量</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >这款游戏存在“毁灭性”的坠落伤害，但玩家可在落地瞬间精准按下按钮触发“反冲击”技能，从而抵消伤害并击飞周围敌人。成功落地后，攻击能量将得到补充，可进行追击。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>◆ 射击、斩击、猎杀敌人，从超高空坠落实现完美着陆！</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >不断击败阻挡去路的虫子。通过成功着陆可以补充能量。交替进行着陆与攻击，将碍事的虫子全部烧毁。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3331090/extras/6b1954e0a79c368966c893f2c04f6e6c.poster.avif?t=1769911795\" width=780 height=334 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3331090/extras/6b1954e0a79c368966c893f2c04f6e6c.webm?t=1769911795\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3331090/extras/6b1954e0a79c368966c893f2c04f6e6c.mp4?t=1769911795\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>◆ 利用从虫子获得的核心来定制机器人</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >花园中栖息着奇异的虫子。击败虫子后获得的核心可用于强化机器人。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>◆ 挑战BOSS</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >击败深藏于关卡深处的强大敌人，获取其力量。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3331090/extras/8cd6516127f7fb28493a86cfcee2d152.poster.avif?t=1769911795\" width=780 height=334 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3331090/extras/8cd6516127f7fb28493a86cfcee2d152.webm?t=1769911795\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3331090/extras/8cd6516127f7fb28493a86cfcee2d152.mp4?t=1769911795\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
